{"tid":2093123,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發：杜魯多稱加拿大正研究對香港實施額外移民措施","createTime":"2020-07-03T15:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T04:19:49.000Z","uid":132625,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff794559116a3c15f2d6c6c92f82d3d74e0b01a","tid":2093123,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"杜魯多稱加拿大正研究對香港實施額外移民措施<br />\n<br />\n加拿大總理杜魯多表示，正研究對香港實施額外的措施，包括移民措施，但他未有交代詳情。加拿大政府又宣布，暫停與香港之間實行的引渡條約。外長商鵬飛發表聲明，禁止出口敏感軍事物品到香港，另外，會對出口到香港敏感商品，採取與出口到中國的相同標準。<br />\n<br />\nRTHK 2020-07-03 23:26:45"},{"pid":"826529071e21a6450efd2c5b7367247bac651941","tid":2093123,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f14844259d1c2e895c41079b35e0c52941558b","tid":2093123,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"度度都話移民<br />\n班候生邊會<br />\n我寧願佢地全部都禁止高官 保皇 黑警入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09659dda332821d01a6e507242dc5bbf5a917d9","tid":2093123,"uid":78243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:35:48.000Z","msg":"中共嗌交部: 加拿大這是搬起石頭砸自己的腳"},{"pid":"e01fa0b3321e9b335671e908708aa49fbb891dc7","tid":2093123,"uid":14936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b5f14844259d1c2e895c41079b35e0c52941558b","tid":2093123,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"度度都話移民<br />\n班候生邊會<br />\n我寧願佢地全部都禁止高官 保皇 黑警入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:45:02.000Z","msg":"我走呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 97後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 